      "created": "2018-08-09T09:48:51.585+0000",
      "description": "If fair scheduler have many queue and each queue have many active applications .\r\n\r\nFor each assignContainer function, we need to sort all the queue, and all the applications in each queue. For a large system,this may be cost too much time. So we can sort the queue and applications\u00a0using a separate thread asynchronous.",
      "priority": {
        "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/priority/4",
        "iconUrl": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/priorities/minor.svg",
        "name": "Minor",
        "id": "4"
      },
      "resolution": null,
