              "displayName": "wan kun",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Asia/Shanghai"
            },
            "body": "[~yufeigu] I'm sorry, I find the sort operation costing too much time in my product environment. But our hadoop version is too old. The newly code change to use TreeSet\u00a0 instead of Collections.sort() method,and only deal with the applications which have resource request.\u00a0The sort operation will be more faster. But this is still a possible problem in the future.\r\n\r\nNow I don't know how many applications will be considered as too many .\r\n\r\n\u00a0\r\n\r\nMaybe this issue can be closed.",
